        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Aegis Overload",
          "description": "300% damage to all enemies and heals all allies for 800% of the user's Attack. All allies will become Enraged and all enemies hit by this attack will become Weakened, this will overwrite any existing Weak or Enrage effects on those units. This attack ignores Skin passive skills and the Counter Stance status effect.\n\nThe user will also have their Power Barrier passive skill reactivated and gain a Power Charge. Usable only if the user's Power Barrier passive skill is deactivated and becomes locked for 100TU after use.\n\n- Enraged units have their Attack increased to 1.5x until the end of their next turn.\n- Weakened units have their Attack reduced to 0.75x until the end of their next turn. The effect of Weakening may be diminished if the affected unit's Attack is increased by other effects and it can be overwritten by Enrage effects.\n- Power Charges cannot stack and will be removed when the user leaves the battlefield.",
