          "name": "Power Barrier",
          "description": "This Barrier will be activated whenever this unit enters battle.\n\nWhile this unit is on the battlefield and this Barrier is activated:\n- Allies gain 35% damage reduction from attacks. This effect can stack with other damage reduction effects such as Armor, but will not stack with itself or other ally Barrier type skills.\n- This unit cannot be defeated by non-attack damage.\n- If this unit takes damage from an attack and survives until after the end of the turn, this unit will heal for 25% of max HP.\n-If this unit would be defeated by an attack, this Barrier will be deactivated and this unit will be Purified and healed for 100% of max HP.\n\nIf this unit's Barrier is deactivated and it would be defeated by an enemy attack or a status effect while having more than 1 HP, it instead survives with 1 HP."
